r Communication Technologies (from 2011 to 2014). He also held various positions in product management, sales and engineering in the Electronic Products group at Littelfuse, Inc., (from 1995 to 2000) and served in various engineering and product management roles in the Optoelectronics Group at Hewlett-Packard Company (from 1988 to 2004). Jeff currently serves as director of Advanced Diamond Technologies, Inc., and as chair for the UIC College of Engineering Advisory Board. He holds a BS in mechanical engineering from UIC.                    UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni       Contact   851 S. Morgan - SEO Rm. 811  Phone: 3129969422  MWilli60@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 